<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5863356453924165210">Anne Cherian was born and raised in Jamshedpur, India. She graduated from Bombay and Bangalore Universities and received graduate degrees in journalism and comparative literature from the University of California, Berkeley. She lives in Los Angeles, California, and visits India regularly.</span>

