          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;He was home. In an environment where he felt loved and comfortable in a way not possible in the United States. And yet, he no longer fit in. He loved living in America, but knew that there, too, he didn't quite fit. It was the classic immigrant dilemma.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
